title: Hypocrisy - Too Drunk To Fuck (Deluxe EP) 2018 ak
description:
contains cover versions of yet two classic punk outlets: The Dead Kennedys Too Drunk To Fuck  and They Lie by The Exploited  
 Also Bonus track Living Dead

Old News On The Dead Kennedys Original Release
The single reached number 36 in the British UK Singles Chart, despite some  refusing to exhibit it due to the title. It was the first single to enter the UK Top 40 which contained the word fuck in the title. It was banned by BBC Radio 1 who refused to broadcast the piece. In the lists of the various rankings, it was routinely referred to as Too Drunk To_____. When it entered the Top 40, the presenter Tony Blackburn referred to the song simply saying A record from a group that calls itself The Dead Kennedys. Good times huh?


Style: Melodic Death and Punk


Tracklist
1. Too Drunk to Fuck (Dead Kennedys Cover)
2. They Lie (The Exploited Cover)	
3. Living Dead (Bonus)
4. Too Drunk To Fuck(Live Dead Kennedys)
